Package: mathrix
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Bryan Wilcutt <bwilcutt@yahoo.com>
Description: Mathematical diagramming tool that uses an autonomous math
 parser called Parser.  This is an engineering solver and a fancy calculator!
 Supports scalar/matrix math, hydraulics, fluid mechanics,
 structural mechanics, thermodynamics, control systems, FFT, and more.

